{
  "chapter": 256,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述项少龙在临淄的多重遭遇。他在前往解府途中遭遇一名持长戟的骑手袭击，凭借冷静判断和风雪配合巧妙化解危机。到达解府后，项少龙发现解子元因逛青楼被妻子善柔发现而惶恐不安，更震惊的是善柔竟是他曾经深爱过的旧情人。两人在厅中独处，善柔认出他并唤出\"少龙\"，项少龙选择默默离开。回到别馆，肖月潭告知吕不韦携韩竭、许商抵达临淄，韩竭作为曹秋道弟子可能为吕不韦拉拢稷下剑士。肖月潭分析齐国王位之争的局势，龙阳君已识破项少龙身份。随后凤菲邀项少龙夜谈，以新曲相赠并对他暧昧试探，项少龙最终克制住自己，以凤菲心属项少龙为由抽身离去。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "来袭者",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈良受死",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今趟拣的真不是时候，不知谁把我昨夜去逛青楼的事告知内子，刚才她大发雷霆，只差未动手打我。\n沈兄快溜，现在说什么她也不会相信的。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "那么过两日我再来找解兄吧！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "快点！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪里走！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "要到哪里去？\n你当我不知道你两个人的把戏吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_jie_quan",
      "text": "解权你给我滚出来，我要你把昨夜的事一字不漏地说出来，万事有我担保。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_quan",
      "speaker_name": "解权",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "少爷！\n小人是被逼的。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "这事全是我想出来的，不关沈兄的事。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你就是那个沈良？看你生得牛高马大，却是胆小如鼠，竟连正眼看人都不敢吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "解夫人可否把其他人请出厅堂，沈某想私下替解兄说两句话。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "这全不关沈兄的事，夫人啊！放沈兄离去好吗？\n要罚，罚我好了。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所有人给我滚出去。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "为夫也要出去吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "为你的什么夫，你第一个给我滚出去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈兄和她说了些什么话？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "嫂子虽是霸道了点，却非是不明白事理的人。\n我向她解释了压迫力愈大，反抗力愈强的道理，假设她任解兄出去胡混，保证不须太久解兄就生厌倦。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我怎会厌倦呢？她怎么答你？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "她说要好好想想。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这是天大的转机，沈兄留下陪我聊聊好吗？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "你最好乖乖的入内去陪伴嫂子，若她以为你又在打鬼主意，说不定连想想都省了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我听你的手下说你会很晚回来，正要离开，咦！\n你的脸色为何这么难看？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "你该听过善柔吧！她是致致的亲姊，曾与我有一段情，现在竟成了解子元的妻子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "又会这么巧的。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "吕不韦今午乘船抵此，同行的尚有韩竭和许商。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "韩竭不是嫪毐的人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "只此一事，可知吕不韦和嫪毐暗中结成一党。\n韩竭乃'稷下剑圣'曹秋道四大弟子之一，有他穿针引线，稷下出身的剑士说不定会站在吕不韦和田单的一边，那形势将截然不同。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "以吕不韦的手段，必可令齐王深信倘改立田建，将会破坏和秦国的关系，若再加上曹秋道站在大王子田生和田单的一边，这场王位之争，输家不是田建才怪。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "谁输谁赢，均是齐人的家事。\n现在我关心的是如何为歌舞姬团的诸位美人儿完成她们的梦想，吕不韦爱怎么搞便怎么搞好了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我很少见到少龙这么意气消沉的，你难道不觉得抽吕不韦的后腿是很有趣的一回事吗？\n你今晚好好睡上一觉，明天醒来时或者会改变想法。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "除非我以项少龙的身份出现，否则如何左右齐王的决定；而且这么一来，等若明请吕不韦来对付我。\n噢！差点忘记告诉你，龙阳君已识穿了我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "若是如此，形势会完全不同。\n现今齐人最怕的是楚人与三晋联手，抑制他们对燕国的野心，只要田单不敢明目张胆的对付你，我们便容易应付多了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "有其利必有其弊，若我公然以项少龙的身份面世，吕不韦、田单，甚至郭开都会暗使手段来对付我，但假若我仍在充当沈良，则又须应付仲孙龙和齐国剑手的挑惹，正是左右做人难。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈先生可认得这段乐章吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这正是由你那些小调变化而来的曲谱，你这人呢！\n竟会听不出来。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "真的一点听不出来，怎会是这样的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人家当然不能一板一眼跟足你的曲调，变化几趟后，便成了这样子！\n欢喜吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "大小姐确是高明，不知是否已为今天贺寿的乐曲全换上新调呢？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你知否人家直到这一刻才惊觉到外面下着大雪，自听到你那些怪调后，凤菲像着了魔的一首接一首把新曲谱出来，想不到竟可如此容易。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "恭喜大小姐。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你究竟是怎样的一个人？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "有手有脚，有眼耳口鼻，和任何人没有什么大分别。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "可是在我眼中，你却像是从仙界下凡的神仙，拯救遇上困苦的世人。\n唉！若真有神仙，那该是多么美丽的一回事。人世间实有着太多事令人生厌，有时我甚至会憎厌自己。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "有很多事确会令人不耐烦的，不过大小姐可知在别人眼中，你正是高不可攀的天之骄子，以能拜倒在你裙下是无比光荣的事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你的用词真怪，什么'高不可攀的天之骄子'、'拜倒裙下'，唉！\n凤菲只是个平凡的人，只有在创作和表演时，我才感到自己有少许的不平凡。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今晚在这里陪人家谈天好吗？\n每逢作成一曲，我都很难入睡，却又苦无倾谈的对象。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "我终是下人，大小姐这样留我在闺房里，不怕别人闲言闲语吗？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你前两晚的勇气到哪里去了？换过是别的男人，在眼前情况，恐怕赶都不肯走吧？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "自得知大小姐的情郎是项少龙后，我愈想愈惊，将来到咸阳时，若有人向他通风报讯，知道我曾在大小姐闺房内留了一晚，就算什么事都没有做过，恐怕亦要小命不保，大小姐以为然否？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "男人不是色胆包天的吗？\n为何你在其他事这么胆大妄为，偏在此事上如此胆小？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "听大小姐的口气，似乎除了想和小人秉烛谈心之外，还有别的下文？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "和你这人说话很有意思，一向以来，只有我凤菲去耍男人，想不到现在却给你来耍我。\n来吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "来什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "先为人家脱掉靴子好吗？管事大人。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "大小姐不是认真的吧？\n这种事开始了就很难中止，那时大小姐想反悔都不行。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈管事你温柔一点好吗？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "羊脂白玉，不外如是。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你若答应我不再往上推移，我便任你就这样占点便宜，当作是报答你令我度过难关的酬劳。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "大小姐这么说，岂非在提醒我要继续深进吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你害死凤菲呢！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "怎样害你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你若令人家爱上你，不是害死人家吗？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "沈良",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "大小姐放心吧！\n只要我想起你是项少龙的人，向天借胆我都不敢碰你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 256,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 364
    }
